<div class="body-container">
  <div class="home-banner">
    <div class="home-title-box">
      <div class="home-banner-title">
        <h1>What Eat</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="home-banner-subtitle">
        <div class="home-banner-subtitle-text">
          <h2>The #1 tool</h2>
          <h2>to plan all</h2>
          <h2>your meals</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="home-banner-subtitle-img">
          <%= image_tag("forkspoon.png", width: '240', align: 'center', alt: "Fork and spoon", class: 'logo-symbol' ) %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="home-button-box">
      <div class="home-button-box-text">
        <h4><b>What Eat</b> is a powerfull tool to help you plan your meals while creating a neat calendar and organizing your grocerie list accordingly. We have a great database with recipes fitting to all dietary restrictions and food preferences.</h4>
        <h4><b>Let us help you eat better!</b></h4>
      </div>
      <div class="home-button-box-buttons">
        <% if user_signed_in? %>
            <button class="button-1"><%= link_to "PLAN MEALS", profile_path(current_user) %></button>
          <% else %>
            <a href="/users/sign_up">
              <button class="button-1">SIGN UP</button>
            </a>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="home-subtitle">
    <h3>Check out some of our recipes:</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="recipe-home-cards-container">
    <div class="recipe-home-cards-line">
      <div class="recipe-home-card">
        <div class="recipe-home-card-content">
          <%= image_tag("ph-card.jpg", justify: 'center', alt: "Salad", class: 'recipe-home-card-image' ) %>
          <div class="recipe-home-card-text">
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-title">
              <h7>Rainbow Salad</h7>
            </div>
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-description">
              <h8> This is a test description for the recipe. You can add as much text as you want, and it will cut it off when the limit is reached.</h8>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="recipe-home-card">
        <div class="recipe-home-card-content">
          <%= image_tag("burguer.jpg", justify: 'center', alt: "Salad", class: 'recipe-home-card-image' ) %>
          <div class="recipe-home-card-text">
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-title">
              <h7>Healthy Sloppy Joes with Lentils</h7>
            </div>
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-description">
              <h8>This version of Sloppy Joes ups the nutrition ante by swapping the meat for lentils, and adding in extra veggies.</h8>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="recipe-home-card">
        <div class="recipe-home-card-content">
          <%= image_tag("dessert.jpg", justify: 'center', alt: "Salad", class: 'recipe-home-card-image' ) %>
          <div class="recipe-home-card-text">
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-title">
              <h7>Rhubarb Strawberry Crunch</h7>
            </div>
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-description">
              <h8>Strawberry and rhubarb make a great flavor team, especially in this crisp.</h8>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="recipe-home-card">
        <div class="recipe-home-card-content">
          <%= image_tag("salmon.jpg", justify: 'center', alt: "Salad", class: 'recipe-home-card-image' ) %>
          <div class="recipe-home-card-text">
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-title">
              <h7>Miso Glazed Salmon Fillet</h7>
            </div>
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-description">
              <h8>Sustainably-fished Atlantic salmon from Kirwin Brothers Fishmongers in Grimsby. Coated in a miso glaze, sprinkled with sesame and baked.</h8>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="recipe-home-card">
        <div class="recipe-home-card-content">
          <%= image_tag("smoky.jpg", justify: 'center', alt: "Salad", class: 'recipe-home-card-image' ) %>
          <div class="recipe-home-card-text">
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-title">
              <h7>Smoky Three-Bean Chilli</h7>
            </div>
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-description">
              <h8> Slow-cooked three-bean chilli in a smoky red pepper and tomato sauce. Served with brown basmati and black rice, and a side of roasted sweet potato wedges.</h8>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="recipe-home-card">
        <div class="recipe-home-card-content">
          <%= image_tag("smoky2.jpg", justify: 'center', alt: "Salad", class: 'recipe-home-card-image' ) %>
          <div class="recipe-home-card-text">
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-title">
              <h7>Smoky Three-Bean</h7>
            </div>
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-description">
              <h8>Slow-cooked three-bean chilli in a smoky red pepper and tomato sauce. Served with Gran Luchito soft shell tacos, and a fresh pineapple and coriander.</h8>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="recipe-home-card">
        <div class="recipe-home-card-content">
          <%= image_tag("dessert2.jpg", justify: 'center', alt: "Salad", class: 'recipe-home-card-image' ) %>
          <div class="recipe-home-card-text">
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-title">
              <h7>Classic Waffles</h7>
            </div>
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-description">
              <h8>You can keep the batter covered in the fridge for up to a week. Just be sure to whisk well before using again.</h8>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="recipe-home-card">
        <div class="recipe-home-card-content">
          <%= image_tag("spaghetti.jpg", justify: 'center', alt: "Salad", class: 'recipe-home-card-image' ) %>
          <div class="recipe-home-card-text">
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-title">
              <h7>Spaghetti Sauce with Ground Beef</h7>
            </div>
            <div class="recipe-home-card-text-description">
              <h8>It is a family favorite and will not be replaced! Serve over any variety of hot cooked pasta.</h8>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
